  <brief_title>Evaluation of Nilotinib In Patients With Advanced Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumor (GIST)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Nilotinib In Patients With Advanced Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumor (GIST) Previously Treated With Imatinib</official_title>
